&lt;p data-start=&quot;1573&quot; data-end=&quot;1591&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1573&quot; data-end=&quot;1591&quot;&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1592&quot; data-end=&quot;2067&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1592&quot; data-end=&quot;1709&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1594&quot; data-end=&quot;1709&quot;&gt;Design, build, test, and release backend systems with high correctness, reliability, and scalability requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1710&quot; data-end=&quot;1786&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1712&quot; data-end=&quot;1786&quot;&gt;Own and maintain key services that power our financial product ecosystem&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1787&quot; data-end=&quot;1883&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1789&quot; data-end=&quot;1883&quot;&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to solve complex engineering and business challenges&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1884&quot; data-end=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1886&quot; data-end=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;Interface with external financial institutions to integrate services and expand capabilities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1981&quot; data-end=&quot;2067&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1983&quot; data-end=&quot;2067&quot;&gt;Contribute to shaping engineering best practices and improving developer workflows&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
