&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;9+ years of experience in Data Security or related areas&amp;nbsp; and expertise in two or more of the following--Cryptography, Kubernetes Security, Web Security, Governance, Privacy, Trust, Safety, Authentication, Identity Management, Access Control, Key Management, Inter-Service Authentication, Secure Application Frameworks, Detection &amp;amp; Response. Experience building systems at large scale internet companies is a huge plus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
